Ocean Showboat Finance Corp, a unit ofShowboat Inc, is raising 180 mln dlrs through an offering ofmortgage-backed bonds due 2002 with an 11-3/8 pct coupon andpar pricing, said sole manager Donaldson, Lufkin and JenretteSecurities Corp.    Moody's Investors Service Inc rates the bonds B-1 andStandard and Poor's Corp rates them B-plus. Reuter&#3;